Participants viewed examples of emotional music and movement.

Author: Beau Sievers

For additional details, refer to:

Sievers, B., Parkinson, C., Kohler, P.J., Hughes, J., Fogelson, S.V., & Wheatley, T. (2018). Visual and auditory brain areas share a neural code for perceived emotion. https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/254961v2

Stimuli are available at https://osf.io/kvbqm/

Contact: beau@beausievers.com
